long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Use this extension to extend to work smarter with Google Data Studio. Do not waste time looking for metrics name on your data sources pages.

Stay on your report, increase productivity.

About Catchr : 
Catchr provides you a way to import all your marketing data directly into Google Data Studio ™. Stop copy / paste from your Facebook Ads, Google Ads ™, Bing Ads, etc. and take back control of your time. 

Catchr is designed to be really simple to use. Choose your data sources, select your metrics and dimensions you want and get all the data you want. 

We support a lot of platform : 
- Facebook Ads
- Facebook Analytics
- Bing Ads
- Microsoft Ads
- Twitter Ads
- LinkedIn Ads
- Pinterest Ads
- TikTok Ads
- LinkedIn Ads
- Google Ads ™

Our support is available every day at https://catchr.io
